{"tid":766521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"牧師分享內地傳教遭打壓經歷 被瑪嘉烈醫院當思覺失調","createTime":"2018-08-03T15:56:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T16:29:13.000Z","uid":6497,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a480edfc408cab16765db946aec97a9ef18a1e1d","tid":766521,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T15:56:37.000Z","msg":"被綁床上牧師指控醫院非法禁錮<br />\n2018/08/03 20:19<br />\n一位牧師聲稱，被醫院的醫生和護士誤當有思覺失調，被綁在床上數小時，指控醫院懷疑非法禁錮。 <br />\n<br />\n國際天糧事工發起人鄔小鶴指，上星期因腸胃炎入住瑪嘉烈醫院，期間他分享自己在內地傳教懷疑被政治打壓，以及與美國特使會面的經歷，出院前他心臟不適，急症室醫生懷疑他有思覺失調，要由精神科護士進一步診斷。 <br />\n<br />\n護士及保安綁起他的四肢在床上，精神科護士其後診斷他沒有精神病，批准出院。他批評醫院沒有足夠理據，粗暴地將他綁起。 <br />\n<br />\n院方回覆指，當時病人精神狀況突然轉變，及出現焦慮，為保障病人安全，為他穿上約束衣物，就不愉快經歷表示慰問，會跟進個案和加強培訓前線醫護人員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/532073/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E8%A2%AB%E7%B6%81%E5%BA%8A%E4%B8%8A%E7%89%A7%E5%B8%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E7%A6%81%E9%8C%AE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F532073%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%25B6%2581%25E5%25BA%258A%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%2589%25A7%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258E%25A7%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E7%25A6%2581%25E9%258C%25AE&d=Y33Wh5SlbbBhD2ieEQzgBMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=435a3618\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F532073%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%25B6%2581%25E5%25BA%258A%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%2589%25A7%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258E%25A7%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E7%25A6%2581%25E9%258C%25AE&h=87e208af\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/532073/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E8%A2%AB%E7%B6%81%E5%BA%8A%E4%B8%8A%E7%89%A7%E5%B8%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E7%A6%81%E9%8C%AE</a>"},{"pid":"6438ff6b79f3250040d32606701a8a56fd918a16","tid":766521,"uid":82532,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T15:57:57.000Z","msg":"講耶穌吖嗱"},{"pid":"6895288b8a59a9278bc2e86082694ae64446365f","tid":766521,"uid":131691,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T15:58:54.000Z","msg":"人哋明明係PTSD個醫生就當人思覺失調<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d89ab7a981b880ff3227c9848059809398ce98f","tid":766521,"uid":37586,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6895288b8a59a9278bc2e86082694ae64446365f","tid":766521,"uid":131691,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T15:58:54.000Z","msg":"人哋明明係PTSD個醫生就當人思覺失調<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T16:01:40.000Z","msg":"想接軌?講支那壞話&quot;被精神病&quot;?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63399d9b02fc4e3ab016d519c0b744c7c8af5467","tid":766521,"uid":550,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T16:02:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以及與美國特使會面的經歷</blockquote><br />\n快啲捉陳云根啦入青山啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdaa9eb7fd5442764d700760454d2ff66584a414","tid":766521,"uid":31780,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T16:03:39.000Z","msg":"走入大陸傳教唔係思覺失調係乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f8617dc7b72cc83f1aa09887bfe33940d8ee94a","tid":766521,"uid":183090,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T16:04:49.000Z","msg":"打壓都覺得正常，但吹撚到同美國特使會面係人都當你癲"},{"pid":"226686db1933e99b2a75ae880c5b65da8547de76","tid":766521,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T16:08:22.000Z","msg":"一般反抗呀想襲撃醫護呀先會綁<br />\n乖乖地接受觀察<br />\ncall屋企人拿證據證明自己所言屬實就會放出院"},{"pid":"30de502efcc66d0569c15e07029f92bc2f05898f","t